ripts/`, `logs/`, `archive/`, `memory/`\n- Added:\n  - `WORKFLOW.md`\n  - `inbox/README.md`\n  - `ops/RUNBOOK.md`\n\n### Important limit\nI **cannot see or control your laptop screen yet** — no laptop/node is connected right now.\n\n### To let me work from your laptop input\nYou need to pair/connect the laptop to OpenClaw (screen/control channel), then I can use it as your input surface.  \nAlso, you can start feeding files immediately by dropping them into `inbox/` and telling me: **“process inbox”**.\n\n### One blocker I hit\nI tried to commit setup changes, but git identity isn’t configured on this machine.  \nRun once in PowerShell:\n\n```powershell\ngit config --global user.name \"Your Name\"\ngit config --global user.email \"you@example.com\"\n```\n\nThen tell me **“commit now”** and I’ll finalize the commit.\n\nIf you want, next I’ll do:\n1) laptop connection checklist, and  \n2) auto-intake script so anything you drop gets sorted automatically.","textSignature":"msg_09754d96df40a1610169a217262fac8191b07ad21b2e45c0fc"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":228,"output":364,"cacheRead":11392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11984,"cost":{"input":0.000399,"output":0.005096,"cacheRead":0.0019936,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0074886}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772230436498}}
